102
00:06:52,330 --> 00:06:54,350
Ten minutes!

103
00:06:56,390 --> 00:06:57,920
Now I have dark circles.

104
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:07,600
Before Keke said yes yesterday,

105
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,150
